name: Early Starkers
description: Early Starkers is the first non-freemint NFT collection of the StarkNet. There are 1234 ranked stars from 1 to 1234, which can be on-chain nameable by the owner. Also, every NFT star has a profile page and unique opportunities for the holders. Early Starkers is the community of pioneers, project owners, builders, researchers, adventurers and holders.
short_description: 1234 Star NFTs on the sky-map enable unique utilities and prove you are an Early Adopter on StarkNet
